				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">elemental transferrence: &lt;type&gt;
<br />
prereq L3 of the matching elemental form.
<br />

<br />
for each type this skill would channel the elemental energy used in transforming yourself to the outside instead of internally to yourself.  it uses the same timer as the elemental forms, so ever 15 mins, or every 30 if you want to keep the illusion up as well.
<br />

<br />
earth: VP like shamans (konckback and root), maybe longer duration
<br />
water: high power heal over time, 1k/tick for 10 or so
<br />
air: either a long stun, or even better...silence, about 15 seconds or so (give it a manaburn style marker so you can't chain it)
<br />
fire: unresistable 7k or so nuke
<br />

<br />
hmm, some of that might be a little big for balancing reasons.  maybe tune it down a little, but when you consider at the absolute max we could use only one of them and only once every 15 mins, meaning just boss fights really.  i'm not seeing this as being hugely overpowered giving the limitations.  it would also inspire raid guilds to maybe have more than one magician in the guild.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
