				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">An old idea I thought well of: summoning a massive throwable spear as a a work-around for a new type of attack.
<br />

<br />
Something like this:
<br />

<br />
LORE, NO RENT, NO DROP
<br />
DELAY: 50  DAMAGE: 500 RANGE: 200
<br />
RANGED, THROWING
<br />
ATK +100
<br />

<br />
The idea is to summon a bolt that can be thrown against magic resistant mobs.
<br />

<br />
Very magey.
<br />

<br />
I remain convinced that a lot of good ideas are possible for mages.
<br />

<br />
Anything but dire charm summoned.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Razamatazz Pizzazz</span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
